data.description: Welcome to your new home in the charming Village 7 neighborhood! This delightful bi-level home offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience & spacious living. With 4 bedrooms & 2 bathrooms, it's an ideal haven for families & those who love to entertain. On the main level, you'll be greeted by a large open living room that's perfect for hosting gatherings & creating lasting memories. Two bedrooms & one bathroom on this level provide ample accommodation for family members & guests. The heart of this home is its well-designed kitchen, featuring a range/oven, refrigerator, microwave, dishwasher & beautiful alder cabinetry. The large island with bar seating is a great spot for casual meals, homework, or chatting with friends & family while preparing delicious meals. The lower level offers a cozy family room, complete with a gas fireplace & a charming brick hearth, making it the perfect place to unwind on chilly evenings or enjoy quality time with loved ones.  Whether you envision a home gym, a home theater, or a playroom, this space will effortlessly adapt to suit your needs. The backyard is an oasis, fully fenced & adorned with mature trees that provide privacy. Whether you're looking to host a barbecue, play a game of catch, or simply relax in the outdoors, this backyard offers it all. Beyond your charming abode, you'll discover that this location has so much to offer. The Village 7 neighborhood is known for its family-friendly atmosphere & you'll find schools, parks & walking paths conveniently nearby. If you're in the mood for dining, shopping, or entertainment, the bustling Powers corridor is just a stone's throw away, providing endless options for leisure & convenience. Plus, with no HOA restrictions, you have the freedom to park your RV, boat, or other recreational vehicles right on your property. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this gem of a home your own. Schedule a visit today and start imagining the life you can create in this fantastic property!
